"""
        Test that the equality/inequality operators return False/True when
        comparing two SplitKey objects with different cryptographic usage
        masks.
        """
a = objects.SplitKey(cryptographic_usage_masks=[enums.
    CryptographicUsageMask.ENCRYPT])
b = objects.SplitKey(cryptographic_usage_masks=[enums.
    CryptographicUsageMask.EXPORT])
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
